#: ../../language/error_codes/E0072.md:1
msgid "E0072"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0072.md:3
msgid "Warning name: `unqualified_local_using`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0072.md:5
msgid "Unqualified local `using` alias."
msgstr "未限定包名的本地 `using` 别名。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0072.md:7
msgid ""
"A private `using` declaration brings names into the local package without"
" their package qualifier. That makes later references harder to update "
"mechanically. Prefer qualified references such as `@pkg.name`, or make "
"the alias public when the package intentionally re-exports it."
msgstr ""
"私有 `using` 声明会把名称以不带包限定符的形式引入当前包。"
"这会让后续引用更难被机械化更新。请优先使用 `@pkg.name` 这样的限定引用；"
"如果当前包确实要重新导出该别名，则将这个别名设为公开。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0072.md:12
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0072.md:14
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"using @test { assert_eq }\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  assert_eq(1 + 1, 2)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0072.md:18
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0072.md:20
msgid "Use the qualified name directly."
msgstr "直接使用带限定符的名称。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0072.md:22
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  @test.assert_eq(1 + 1, 2)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
